Neglected housewife Kaylani Lei wants to spice up her marriage, so she decorates her naked body in juicy fruit and waits for her hungry husband to come home from work. But instead of her husband she's greeted by her husband's assistant, who is just stopping by to grab her husband an overnight bag. Kaylani is no fool, she knows her husband is having an affair. And if he's not going to appreciate her forbidden fruits, maybe his assistant will!
